    "display_name": "Card Styling Challenge",
    "long_instructions": "#Card Styling Challenge\r\n\r\nWith the help of AI, improve how the content cards look and feel. This can include:\r\n   - Borders and corners: border shape and color\r\n   - Shadows: consistent shadows and elevation\r\n   - Spacing: padding inside cards, gap between elements\r\n   - Image fit: no stretching; consistent shape\r\n\r\n::: details [Example AI Style Prompts]\r\nTry any of these example prompts:\r\n- *Style the cards with rounded corners that match the site’s radius tokens.*\r\n- *Let’s revise the card style to have consistent padding and vertical spacing between image, title, text, and button.*\r\n- *Fix the images so they don’t stretch and have a consistent aspect ratio.*\r\n- *On hover, raise the card slightly and increase the shadow; keep usable contrast.*\r\n:::",
    "bubble_choice_description": "Improve the look of content cards. ",
    "thumbnail_url": "https://images.code.org/81685e6a3a6cc9bebd7ab8a6101f4467-website-design.png",
    "start_sources": {
      "folders": {
      },
      "files": {
        "1": {
          "id": "1",
          "name": "index.html",
          "language": "html",
          "contents": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Volunteer Board — Card Styling Challenge</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\" />\n</head>\n<body>\n  <a class=\"skip-link\" href=\"#main\">Skip to content</a>\n\n  <header class=\"site-header\">\n    <div class=\"container header-inner\">\n      <h1 class=\"brand\">Volunteer Board</h1>\n      <nav aria-label=\"Primary\">\n        <ul class=\"nav\">\n          <li><a href=\"#env\">Environment</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#tutor\">Tutoring</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#events\">Events</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </nav>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <main id=\"main\">\n    <section class=\"hero container\">\n      <h2>Find a way to help this month</h2>\n      <p class=\"lede\">Pick a project, bring a friend, make an impact.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"cards container\" aria-label=\"Opportunities\">\n      <!-- Card 1 -->\n      <article class=\"card\">\n        <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/forest/560/340\" alt=\"Forest clean-up\" />\n        <div class=\"card-body\">\n          <h3>Trail Clean-Up</h3>\n          <p>Join the weekend crew to remove debris and mark new paths in the north woods.</p>\n          <div class=\"tags\">\n            <span class=\"tag\">Environment</span>\n            <span class=\"tag\">Outdoors</span>\n          </div>\n          <a class=\"btn\" href=\"#join-1\">Join Us</a>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n\n      <!-- Card 2 (longer text) -->\n      <article class=\"card\">\n        <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/library/420/500\" alt=\"Library tutoring\" />\n        <div class=\"card-body\">\n          <h3>Library Tutoring</h3>\n          <p>Support elementary students with reading and homework. Materials provided; training on day one.</p>\n          <div class=\"tags\">\n            <span class=\"tag\">Tutoring</span>\n            <span class=\"tag\">After School</span>\n          </div>\n          <a class=\"btn\" href=\"#join-2\">Join Us</a>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n\n      <!-- Card 3 -->\n      <article class=\"card\">\n        <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/community/720/280\" alt=\"Community event\" />\n        <div class=\"card-body\">\n          <h3>Community Festival</h3>\n          <p>Help set up booths and guide visitors. Great for first-time volunteers.</p>\n          <div class=\"tags\">\n            <span class=\"tag\">Events</span>\n          </div>\n          <a class=\"btn\" href=\"#join-3\">Join Us</a>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n\n      <!-- Card 4 -->\n      <article class=\"card\">\n        <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/foodbank/500/300\" alt=\"Food bank\" />\n        <div class=\"card-body\">\n          <h3>Food Bank Packing</h3>\n          <p>Sort and pack donations for local families. Lifting required; bring closed-toe shoes.</p>\n          <div class=\"tags\">\n            <span class=\"tag\">Food</span>\n            <span class=\"tag\">Logistics</span>\n          </div>\n          <a class=\"btn\" href=\"#join-4\">Join Us</a>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer class=\"site-footer container\">\n      <p>© 2025 Volunteer Board</p>\n    </footer>\n  </main>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
          "active": false,
          "folderId": "0"
        },
        "2": {
          "id": "2",
          "name": "styles.css",
          "language": "css",
          "contents": "   Everything looks plain so students can clearly improve it. */\n\n/* Tokens */\n:root{\n  --accent: #16a34a;\n  --text: #1f2937;\n  --muted: #6b7280;\n  --bg: #f6f7fb;\n  --surface: #ffffff;\n  --border: #d1d5db;   /* dull gray border */\n\n  --s-2: 8px;\n  --s-4: 16px;\n  --s-6: 24px;\n}\n\n*{ box-sizing:border-box; }\nhtml,body{ margin:0; padding:0; }\nbody{\n  font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial;\n  color: var(--text);\n  background: var(--bg);\n  line-height: 1.5;\n}\nimg{ max-width:100%; display:block; }\nh1,h2,h3{ margin:0 0 var(--s-2); line-height:1.2; }\np{ margin:0 0 var(--s-2); }\na{ color: var(--accent); text-decoration:none; }\n\n/* Header + layout baseline */\n.container{ width:min(100%,1080px); margin:0 auto; padding:0 var(--s-4); }\n.site-header{ background:var(--surface); border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); }\n.header-inner{ display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; padding: var(--s-4) 0; }\n.brand{ margin:0; }\n.nav{ display:flex; gap: var(--s-4); list-style:none; padding:0; margin:0; }\n.nav a{ color:var(--text); }\n\n.hero{ padding: var(--s-6) 0; }\n.lede{ color: var(--muted); }\n\n/* Cards grid */\n.cards{\n  display:grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));\n  gap: var(--s-4);\n  padding: var(--s-6) 0;\n}\n\n/* ---- CARD BASE ---- */\n.card{\n  background: var(--surface);\n  border: 1px solid var(--border);\n  border-radius: 0;           /* square edges */\n  /* ❌ no padding – cramped content */\n  padding: 0;\n  /* ❌ no shadow – totally flat */\n  box-shadow: none;\n}\n\n/* ---- IMAGE ---- */\n.card > img{\n  width:100%;\n  height:160px;                /* inconsistent with aspect ratio */\n  object-fit: fill;            /* distortion visible */\n  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n}\n\n/* ---- CARD BODY ---- */\n.card-body{\n  /* ❌ zero padding → text hugs edges */\n  padding: 0;\n  margin: 0;\n}\n.card h3{\n  margin: 6px 0 4px;           /* cramped */\n  font-size: 1rem;\n}\n.card p{\n  color: var(--muted);\n  font-size: .9rem;\n  margin: 0 0 6px;\n}\n\n/* ---- TAGS ---- */\n.tags{\n  display:flex;\n  gap: 4px;\n  margin: 4px 0;\n}\n.tag{\n  border: 1px solid var(--border);\n  padding: 2px 4px;            /* tiny */\n  font-size: .75rem;\n  border-radius: 0;            /* sharp chips */\n  background: transparent;\n}\n\n/* ---- BUTTON ---- */\n.btn{\n  display:inline-block;\n  padding: 0;                  /* looks like plain text */\n  border: none;\n  background: none;\n  color: var(--accent);\n  text-align:left;\n  font-weight:600;\n  cursor:pointer;\n  margin: 4px 0;\n}\n\n/* Footer */\n.site-footer{\n  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);\n  padding: var(--s-6) 0;\n  text-align:center;\n  color: var(--muted);\n}\n",
          "folderId": "0",
          "active": true
        }
      },
      "openFiles": [
        "1",
        "2"
      ]
    },
